{
  "stem": "7069.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the neighborhood that we lived in Berlin was called the Wedding, which is really a laborer-- an area where the labor force mostly lived.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Heavily communist-- communistic infested, so to speak, if I may say that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was-- it was not at all predominantly Jewish neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a few Jewish people living here and there, yes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But not-- not predominantly, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, our mother was a wonderful woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's no question about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had a lot of tough luck in her life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was a-- a dressmaker, a seamstress dressmaker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, had never made much money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We really lived in very dire circumstances most of the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As I said, my father wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so-- But she was always a happy woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Did a lot of singing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a lot of singing going on in the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she and I and my brother, we would sing trios.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were a very happy family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In fact, in the summertime, when the windows were open, some of the people out there would holler, more, more, more!",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so we were-- we were, as I say, even though in-- in financial misery at times, we were a happy family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was an excellent cook.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- and a-- and a super neat housekeeper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When she scrubbed the floors, which were done at those days in Germany, there was no paint over the floor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the beautiful wood was to be shown in the kitchen, particularly boards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She would scrub the floor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then she would lay out paper so it doesn't get dirty so quick again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And to wash our hands was on a steady-- steady order.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And cleanliness was just-- oh, gosh.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
